    <title>GitHub Pages 靜態網站</title>
    <link href="http://joemacaco.github.io/2017/07/23/GitHub%20Pages/"/>
    <id>http://joemacaco.github.io/2017/07/23/GitHub Pages/</id>
    <published>2017-07-23T10:18:07.000Z</published>
    <updated>2017-07-23T14:43:08.208Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>為了架設個人Blog所以才關注到，Github有提供將個人projects直接轉換靜態網站的服務，一些簡單的介紹可以觀看官方介紹影片<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2MsN8gpT6jY" target="_blank" rel="external">What is GitHub Pages?</a></p>
<p><strong>GitHub Pages</strong>官網底下有推薦使用<strong>Jekyll</strong>去建構靜態網頁，不過是使用<strong>Ruby</strong>去操作的，所以最後選擇使用<strong>Hexo</strong>當這次的介紹，<strong>Hexo</strong>官網也有繁體中文的文件所以建構起來也比較容易</p>
<a id="more"></a>
<p>為了架設個人Blog所以才關注到，Github有提供將個人projects直接轉換靜態網站的服務，一些簡單的介紹可以觀看官方介紹影片<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2MsN8gpT6jY" target="_blank" rel="external">What is GitHub Pages?</a></p>
<p><strong>GitHub Pages</strong>官網底下有推薦使用<strong>Jekyll</strong>去建構靜態網頁，不過是使用<strong>Ruby</strong>去操作的，所以最後選擇使用<strong>Hexo</strong>當這次的介紹，<strong>Hexo</strong>官網也有繁體中文的文件所以建構起來也比較容易</p>
<h3 id="Github-Setup"><a href="#Github-Setup" class="headerlink" title="Github Setup"></a>Github Setup</h3><p>Create a repository<br>Clone the repository<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">~$ git <span class="built_in">clone</span> https://github.com/username/username.github.io</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>Hello World<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">~$ <span class="built_in">cd</span> username.github.io</div><div class="line">~$ <span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="string">"Hello World"</span> &gt; index.html</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>Fire up a browser and go to <code>https://username.github.io.</code></p>
<h3 id="Hexo-Setup"><a href="#Hexo-Setup" class="headerlink" title="Hexo Setup"></a>Hexo Setup</h3><h4 id="安裝需求"><a href="#安裝需求" class="headerlink" title="安裝需求"></a>安裝需求</h4><p>安裝前先檢查是否已經安裝 <a href="https://nodejs.org/en/" target="_blank" rel="external">Node.js</a> 和 <a href="https://git-scm.com/" target="_blank" rel="external">Git</a><br>安裝Hexo<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ npm install -g hexo-cli</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<h4 id="建立"><a href="#建立" class="headerlink" title="建立"></a>建立</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ hexo init &lt;blog name&gt;</div><div class="line">$ <span class="built_in">cd</span> &lt;blog name&gt;</div><div class="line">$ npm install</div><div class="line">$ npm install --save hexo-renderer-jade hexo-generator-feed hexo-generator-sitemap hexo-browsersync hexo-generator-archive</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h4 id="指令"><a href="#指令" class="headerlink" title="指令"></a>指令</h4><h5 id="init"><a href="#init" class="headerlink" title="init"></a>init</h5><p>初始化建立所有檔案<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ hexo init [folder]</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<h5 id="new"><a href="#new" class="headerlink" title="new"></a>new</h5><p>建立寫作檔案<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ hexo new [layout] &lt;title&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<h5 id="generate"><a href="#generate" class="headerlink" title="generate"></a>generate</h5><p>產生靜態檔案<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ hexo generate</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<h5 id="server"><a href="#server" class="headerlink" title="server"></a>server</h5><p>在local查看Blog <code>http://localhost:4000/</code><br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ hexo server</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<h5 id="deploy"><a href="#deploy" class="headerlink" title="deploy"></a>deploy</h5><p>部署網站<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ hexo deploy</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<h4 id="配置"><a href="#配置" class="headerlink" title="配置"></a>配置</h4><p>修改_config.yml設定值，去設定網站的一些顯示設定<br>themes裡面的_config.yml則是針對樣式的設定值</p>
<h4 id="佈署"><a href="#佈署" class="headerlink" title="佈署"></a>佈署</h4><p>repo設定在_config.yml內<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">deploy:</div><div class="line">  type: git</div><div class="line">  repo: &lt;repository url&gt;</div><div class="line">  branch: [branch]</div><div class="line">  message: [message]</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>佈署網站<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</div><div class="line">$ hexo deploy</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<h3 id="Github-佈署"><a href="#Github-佈署" class="headerlink" title="Github 佈署"></a>Github 佈署</h3><p>一般佈署完成後Github Pages網址為 <code>https://username.github.io</code><br>如果想要使用 <code>https://username.github.io/repo_name</code> 網址則需要一些額外設定</p>
<ul>
<li><p>clone要建立page的repo</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ git <span class="built_in">clone</span> https://github.com/username/blog.git</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p>建立<code>gh-pages</code>的branch</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ git checkout --orphan gh-pages</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p>push到github</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ git push origin gh-pages</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="參考連結"><a href="#參考連結" class="headerlink" title="參考連結"></a>參考連結</h3><ul>
<li><a href="https://pages.github.com/" target="_blank" rel="external">GitHub Pages</a></li>
<li><a href="https://jekyllrb.com/" target="_blank" rel="external">Jekyll</a></li>
<li><a href="https://hexo.io/zh-tw/" target="_blank" rel="external">Hexo</a></li>
<li><a href="https://help.github.com/articles/creating-project-pages-using-the-command-line/" target="_blank" rel="external">creating-project-pages-using-the-command-line</a></li>
</ul>
]]></content>
    
