    <title>Sublime Text 3 Setup</title>
    <link href="http://joemacaco.github.io/2015/04/22/Sublim%20Text%203%20Setup/"/>
    <id>http://joemacaco.github.io/2015/04/22/Sublim Text 3 Setup/</id>
    <published>2015-04-22T07:52:07.000Z</published>
    <updated>2017-07-23T10:49:10.184Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Sublime Text 3 Setup<br>以下介紹一些基礎設定，跟一些好用的插件介紹<br>下載 <a href="http://www.sublimetext.com/3" target="_blank" rel="external">Sublime 3</a></p>
<a id="more"></a>
<p>以下介紹一些基礎設定，跟一些好用的插件介紹</p>
<h3 id="安裝流程"><a href="#安裝流程" class="headerlink" title="安裝流程"></a>安裝流程</h3><p>下載 <a href="http://www.sublimetext.com/3" target="_blank" rel="external">Sublime 3</a><br>安裝記的勾選 <strong>Add to explorer context menu</strong> 才能使用右鍵開啟選項<br><img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/-xIUXxFsCtCY/VVLmHeI4sVI/AAAAAAAAALg/yNHfHBcxiWE/w513-h398-no/setup.png" alt="setup1"><br>安裝完成後就安裝 <a href="https://packagecontrol.io/installation" target="_blank" rel="external">Package Control</a> 使用 <code>Ctrl+` </code> 開啟 Sublime控制台 輸入安裝指令送出<br><img src="https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/-JAypU1sc160/VVLmH_lzjrI/AAAAAAAAALs/fRyCVi3r4tQ/w1274-h685-no/setuppackagecontrol.png" alt="setup2"><br>安裝完成後重開 <strong>Sublime</strong> 使用<code>Ctrl+Shift+P</code>開啟 <strong>Package Control</strong> 輸入<code>Install</code><br><img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/-B-zDjygskeo/VVLniJn7t6I/AAAAAAAAAMQ/Edo4r2wUWsQ/w1274-h685-no/install.png" alt="setup3"></p>
<h3 id="環境設定"><a href="#環境設定" class="headerlink" title="環境設定"></a>環境設定</h3><p>開啟檔案目錄：<code>File -&gt; Open Folder</code><br>顯示目前開啟的檔案：<code>View -&gt; Side Bar -&gt; Show Open Files</code><br>修改Sublime樣式：<code>Preferences -&gt; Color Scheme -&gt; Colorsublime-Themes</code><br>修改字體大小：<code>Preferences -&gt; Settings-User -&gt; &quot;font_size&quot;: 14</code><br>取消自動偵測 <code>Tab Size</code><br>修改設定：<code>Preferences -&gt; Settings</code><br>Settings-Default 則是預設的設定不可直接修改，可以看裡面有什麼設定，需要透過user的設定去修改，如下<br><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div><div class="line">15</div><div class="line">16</div><div class="line">17</div><div class="line">18</div><div class="line">19</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">&#123;</div><div class="line">  <span class="string">"Seti_SB_big"</span>: <span class="literal">true</span>,</div><div class="line">  <span class="string">"caret_style"</span>: <span class="string">"phase"</span>, <span class="comment">// 游標模式</span></div><div class="line">  <span class="string">"color_scheme"</span>: <span class="string">"Packages/User/SublimeLinter/Monokai (SL).tmTheme"</span>,</div><div class="line">  <span class="string">"default_line_ending"</span>: <span class="string">"unix"</span>, <span class="comment">// 預設換行符號</span></div><div class="line">  <span class="string">"detect_indentation"</span>: <span class="literal">false</span>, <span class="comment">//取消自動偵測 Tab Size</span></div><div class="line">  <span class="string">"draw_white_space"</span>: <span class="string">"all"</span>, <span class="comment">//顯示空白</span></div><div class="line">  <span class="string">"font_size"</span>: <span class="number">14</span>,</div><div class="line">  <span class="string">"highlight_line"</span>: <span class="literal">true</span>,</div><div class="line">  <span class="string">"ignored_packages"</span>:</div><div class="line">  [</div><div class="line">    <span class="string">"Vintage"</span></div><div class="line">  ],</div><div class="line">  <span class="string">"show_encoding"</span>: <span class="literal">true</span>, <span class="comment">// 顯示檔案編碼</span></div><div class="line">  <span class="string">"tab_size"</span>: <span class="number">2</span>,</div><div class="line">  <span class="string">"show_line_endings"</span>: <span class="literal">true</span>,</div><div class="line">  <span class="string">"theme"</span>: <span class="string">"Seti_orig.sublime-theme"</span>,</div><div class="line">  <span class="string">"translate_tabs_to_spaces"</span>: <span class="literal">true</span> <span class="comment">// 按下tab時轉換成space</span></div><div class="line">&#125;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<h3 id="安裝插件"><a href="#安裝插件" class="headerlink" title="安裝插件"></a>安裝插件</h3><p>其它插件：<a href="http://colorsublime.com/" target="_blank" rel="external">Colorsublime</a>、<strong>jQuery</strong>、<strong>JsFormat</strong>、<strong>Sass</strong>、<strong>SCSS</strong>、<strong>SublimeTmpl</strong>、<strong>SFTP</strong></p>
<h4 id="Colorsublime"><a href="#Colorsublime" class="headerlink" title="Colorsublime"></a>Colorsublime</h4><p>更改<strong>Sublime</strong>的樣式，安裝完成後在安裝版型<br><img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/-x5469rkHHM8/VVM1XtUZA_I/AAAAAAAAAN0/KLRe8VJKacc/w1274-h685-no/installcolor.png" alt="setup4"></p>
<h4 id="Emmet"><a href="#Emmet" class="headerlink" title="Emmet"></a>Emmet</h4><p>在<strong>html</strong>時如果輸入<code>input-pw + Tab</code>就會自動轉換成<code>&lt;input class=&quot;form-control&quot; type=&quot;password&quot;&gt;</code><br><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div><div class="line">15</div><div class="line">16</div><div class="line">17</div><div class="line">18</div><div class="line">19</div><div class="line">20</div><div class="line">21</div><div class="line">22</div><div class="line">23</div><div class="line">24</div><div class="line">25</div><div class="line">26</div><div class="line">27</div><div class="line">28</div><div class="line">29</div><div class="line">30</div><div class="line">31</div><div class="line">32</div><div class="line">33</div><div class="line">34</div><div class="line">35</div><div class="line">36</div><div class="line">37</div><div class="line">38</div><div class="line">39</div><div class="line">40</div><div class="line">41</div><div class="line">42</div><div class="line">43</div><div class="line">44</div><div class="line">45</div><div class="line">46</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">&#123;</div><div class="line">  <span class="string">"snippets"</span> : &#123;</div><div class="line">    <span class="string">"html"</span> : &#123;  <span class="comment">//在html中啟用</span></div><div class="line">      <span class="string">"snippets"</span> : &#123;</div><div class="line">        <span class="string">"viewport"</span> : <span class="string">"&lt;meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width,initial-scale=1\"&gt;"</span>,</div><div class="line">        <span class="string">"keywords"</span> : <span class="string">"&lt;meta name=\"keywords\" content=\"\"&gt;"</span>,</div><div class="line">        <span class="string">"description"</span> : <span class="string">"&lt;meta name=\"description\" content=\"\"&gt;"</span>,</div><div class="line">        <span class="string">"container"</span> : <span class="string">"&lt;div class=\"container\"&gt;\n\t&lt;div class=\"row\"&gt;\n\t&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;"</span>,</div><div class="line">        <span class="string">"row"</span> : <span class="string">"&lt;div class=\"row\"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;"</span>,</div><div class="line">        <span class="string">"col1"</span> : <span class="string">"&lt;div class=\"col-sm-1\"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;"</span>,</div><div class="line">        <span class="string">"col2"</span> : <span class="string">"&lt;div class=\"col-sm-2\"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;"</span>,</div><div class="line">        <span class="string">"col3"</span> : <span class="string">"&lt;div class=\"col-sm-3\"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;"</span>,</div><div class="line">        <span class="string">"col4"</span> : <span class="string">"&lt;div class=\"col-sm-4\"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;"</span>,</div><div class="line">        <span class="string">"col5"</span> : <span class="string">"&lt;div class=\"col-sm-5\"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;"</span>,</div><div class="line">        <span class="string">"col6"</span> : <span class="string">"&lt;div class=\"col-sm-6\"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;"</span>,</div><div class="line">        <span class="string">"col7"</span> : <span class="string">"&lt;div class=\"col-sm-7\"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;"</span>,</div><div class="line">        <span class="string">"col8"</span> : <span class="string">"&lt;div class=\"col-sm-8\"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;"</span>,</div><div class="line">        <span class="string">"col9"</span> : <span class="string">"&lt;div class=\"col-sm-9\"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;"</span>,</div><div class="line">        <span class="string">"col10"</span> : <span class="string">"&lt;div class=\"col-sm-10\"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;"</span>,</div><div class="line">        <span class="string">"col11"</span> : <span class="string">"&lt;div class=\"col-sm-11\"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;"</span>,</div><div class="line">        <span class="string">"col12"</span> : <span class="string">"&lt;div class=\"col-sm-12\"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;"</span>,</div><div class="line">        <span class="string">"icon"</span> : <span class="string">"&lt;link rel=\"icon\" href=\"\"&gt;"</span>,</div><div class="line">        <span class="string">"font-awesome"</span> : <span class="string">"&lt;link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"//maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/font-awesome/4.3.0/css/font-awesome.min.css\"&gt;"</span>,</div><div class="line">        <span class="string">"bootstrap-css"</span> : <span class="string">"&lt;link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.2/css/bootstrap.min.css\"&gt;"</span>,</div><div class="line">        <span class="string">"bootstrap-theme"</span> : <span class="string">"&lt;link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.2/css/bootstrap-theme.min.css\"&gt;"</span>,</div><div class="line">        <span class="string">"bootstrap-js"</span> : <span class="string">"&lt;script src=\"https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.2/js/bootstrap.min.js\"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;"</span>,</div><div class="line">        <span class="string">"jquery1-8-3"</span> : <span class="string">"&lt;script src=\"https://code.jquery.com/jquery-1.8.3.min.js\"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;"</span>,</div><div class="line">        <span class="string">"jquery1-11-1"</span> : <span class="string">"&lt;script src=\"https://code.jquery.com/jquery-1.11.1.min.js\"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;"</span>,</div><div class="line">        <span class="string">"select"</span> : <span class="string">"&lt;select class=\"form-control\"&gt;\n\t&lt;option&gt;\n\t&lt;/option&gt;\n&lt;/select&gt;"</span>,</div><div class="line">        <span class="string">"form-inline"</span> : <span class="string